# title: Mainframe Mystery Starter
# recommended_speed: normal
# category: premium retro mainframe ambience
# creator: Nerd Scroll
# license: included starter pack
# notes: fictional green-screen mystery; cosmetic text only

[PACK] Mainframe Mystery Starter :: Premium Edition
[MODE] scrolling green-screen archive
[STYLE] JCL / batch reports / impossible timestamps / printer-room suspense
[SAFETY] scene text only; no real system actions
[RENDER] normal speed feels like a real operator session; slow speed feels haunted

