SCREEN 0003 :: COBOL-LIKE PROGRAM LISTING
======================================================================

       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ARCHIVE13.
       AUTHOR. NIGHT-SHIFT.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT VAULT-FILE ASSIGN TO 'DRAWER-13'.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  VAULT-FILE.
       01  VAULT-RECORD.
           05  VR-TIMESTAMP        PIC X(19).
           05  VR-ROOM-CODE        PIC X(08).
           05  VR-KNOCK-COUNT      PIC 9(03).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DOOR-STATUS         PIC X(06) VALUE 'LOCKED'.
       01  WS-SHADOW-COUNT        PIC 9(03) VALUE 007.
       01  WS-TOMORROW-FLAG       PIC X(03) VALUE 'YES'.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY 'OPENING ARCHIVE DRAWER 13'.
           DISPLAY 'VERIFYING TIME BEFORE IT HAPPENS'.
           STOP RUN.

